articles.title: Kuno: Female cheetah dies from mating injuries in India - BBC
articles.description: Three of the 20 big cats brought to India from Namibia and South Africa are now dead.
articles.content:
A female cheetah has died in Kuno National Park in India's Madhya Pradesh state, taking the number of the big cats found dead to three since March.
